    "id": "nce1-039-040-don-t-drop-it",
    "title": "Lesson 39: Don't drop it!",
    "audioFilename": "039&040－Don't Drop It.mp3",
    "duration": 69.564,
    "language": "en"
  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "start": 0.46,
      "end": 2.16,
      "text": "Lesson 39.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第39课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "start": 3.36,
      "end": 4.8,
      "text": "Don't Drop It.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "别摔了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "start": 6.44,
      "end": 10.42,
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "start": 12.6,
      "end": 16.2,
      "text": "Where does Sam put the vase in the end?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "最后萨姆把花瓶放在哪里？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "start": 18.55,
      "end": 22.65,
      "text": "What are you going to do with that vase, Penny?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "彭妮，你打算怎么处理那个花瓶？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "start": 23.97,
      "end": 27.65,
      "text": "I'm going to put it on this table, Sam.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我准备把它放在这张桌子上，萨姆。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "start": 28.87,
      "end": 30.33,
      "text": "Don't do that.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "别那么做。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "start": 31.33,
      "end": 32.75,
      "text": "Give it to me.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "把它给我。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "start": 33.77,
      "end": 36.27,
      "text": "What are you going to do with it?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你准备怎么处理它？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "start": 37.47,
      "end": 42.17,
      "text": "I'm going to put it here, in front of the window.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我准备把它放在这里，窗户前面。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "start": 43.07,
      "end": 43.85,
      "text": "Be careful.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "小心。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "start": 44.83,
      "end": 46.09,
      "text": "Don't drop it.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "别把它摔了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "start": 47.23,
      "end": 49.47,
      "text": "Don't put it there, Sam.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "别把它放在那里，萨姆。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "start": 50.37,
      "end": 52.97,
      "text": "Put it here, on this shelf.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "把它放在这里，这个架子上。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "start": 53.97,
      "end": 55.93,
      "text": "There we are.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "好了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "start": 56.75,
      "end": 58.45,
      "text": "It's a lovely vase.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这个花瓶真漂亮。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "start": 59.51,
      "end": 62.31,
      "text": "Those flowers are lovely, too.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "那些花也很漂亮。"
      }
    }
  ]
}
